sequenceDiagram
autonumber
actor U as User
participant FE as Frontend
participant Guard as Auth/Permission Guard
participant PS as PermissionService
participant Repo as ProjectRepository
participant DS as DomainService

U->>FE: Send request to project resource
FE->>Guard: Request + access token
Guard->>Guard: Read authenticated user from JWT
alt User is invalid
  Guard-->>FE: 401 Unauthorized
  FE-->>U: Ask user to sign in again
else User is valid
  Guard->>Repo: Load target project/resource
  alt Resource does not exist
    Repo-->>Guard: Not found
    Guard-->>FE: 404 Not Found
  else Resource exists
    Repo-->>Guard: Project/resource data
    Guard->>PS: Check system role and membership
    PS->>Repo: Load project membership
    Repo-->>PS: Project role
    alt System ADMIN or sufficient project role
      PS-->>Guard: Allow
      Guard->>DS: Execute domain operation
      DS-->>Guard: Operation result
      Guard-->>FE: 200 OK
      FE-->>U: Return response
    else Insufficient permission
      PS-->>Guard: Deny
      Guard-->>FE: 403 Forbidden
    end
  end
end
